result.name: Fixed Version of pink anime stuff - Roblox
result.description: This is the fixed version of the original, the background works and this will work on both light and dark mode, and I renamed the style cause people that know better told me it ain't gyaru. Credits go to >Yashme< for the colour choices. Nitroplus is the creator of Super Sonico the girl on the left. The blue haired girl on the right side is Sayumi Ureshino from an anime called 'A Good Librarian Like a Good Shepherd' & the girl with her mouth open at the bottom of the image is Ink Nijihara from Moetan. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
result.notes: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Tablets/iPads or phones won't work, Chrome & Opera are the only browsers that work well with the extension. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi.
